  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个日程管理系统的时序图，核心流程有三个：用户添加事件、设置提醒、以及按天查看事件。参与者包括User、SchedulerApp、Event、EventDAO、Reminder和ReminderService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "Reminder",
        "ReminderService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下添加事件的流程：User向SchedulerApp发起请求，SchedulerApp创建Event对象（包含title、description、start_time、end_time这些属性），然后Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法持久化，最后返回确认给SchedulerApp。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "title",
        "description",
        "start_time",
        "end_time",
        "add_event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Event到EventDAO的调用是异步返回，用虚线箭头。接下来是设置提醒的流程：用户通过SchedulerApp创建Reminder，Reminder需要关联event_id和send_time，然后交给ReminderService去调度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Reminder",
        "event_id",
        "send_time",
        "ReminderService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，添加事件和设置提醒两条主线已经画好了。现在处理第三个功能——查看事件。这里应该是User向SchedulerApp请求查看某天的日程，SchedulerApp直接查询EventDAO的get_events_for_day方法，传入day参数，返回事件列表后再展示给用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "EventDAO",
        "get_events_for_day",
        "day"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，这里有个问题。SchedulerApp不应该直接调用EventDAO，按照我们之前的分层设计，应该让Event对象去和DAO交互。不过……不对，查看事件是查询操作，不需要创建Event实例。让我想想——实际上在这个场景下，SchedulerApp直接访问EventDAO是合理的，因为返回的是事件列表而非单个对象。保持你现在的画法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SchedulerApp",
        "EventDAO",
        "Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，三条消息流都用虚线返回：EventDAO返回\"Event added\"给SchedulerApp，ReminderService返回\"Reminder scheduled\"，最后EventDAO返回事件列表，SchedulerApp再\"Display events\"给User。所有异步返回都处理成虚线箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "ReminderService",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有一点，参与者的命名建议用缩写别名，比如EventDAO显示为EVDAO，ReminderService显示为RMS，这样图更简洁。Event显示为EV，Reminder显示为RM。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "EVDAO",
        "ReminderService",
        "RMS",
        "Event",
        "EV",
        "Reminder",
        "RM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整别名：UA代表User，SA代表SchedulerApp，EV代表Event，EVDAO代表EventDAO，RM代表Reminder，RMS代表ReminderService。三条用户请求分别标注为\"Request add event\"、\"Request schedule reminder\"和\"Request view events\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UA",
        "SA",
        "EV",
        "EVDAO",
        "RM",
        "RMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个时序图完整覆盖了日程管理的核心交互。三个用户场景清晰，分层结构合理，可以定稿了。",
